name: Frida Punk 017 - Money Shot
description:
Fun fact: Fridas image, as well as her husbands (Diego Rivera) appeared on the 500 pesos note in 2010. The bill commemorated  the 100th anniversary of the Mexican Revolution. It featured the Rivera quote:

“It has been said that the revolution does not need art, but that art needs the revolution. That is not true. The revolution needs revolutionary art.”
